Description
-----------

Page files are used to specify the actual content for the website and
are written using WebPage Format. Therefore they contain the content for
the web page and, optionally, meta information.

*In contrast* to other handled files, page files can never be
unlocalized! If they have no language set, the default language
specified using the Core/Configuration:lang parameter is used. This
means that for the default language set to English and a source filename
`index.page`, the language meta information is automatically set to
English.
